<Content>A place to relax, but could be better Hello everyone, we are from Staten Isalnd, NY and we stood at the Hilton in Ponce from 3/17/05 to 3/21/05. It was a great place to relax and the staff was very friendly. The food was good, but the prices were very expensive. However, there was not much to do as far as acivities were concerned. We actually missed out on a couple of acitivities within the near by vicintiy of the hotel that we normally wouldnt have missed if we were directed to or informed correctly by staff members. One must ask the front desk staff of any activities that one might be interested in doing such as snorkling, party boat rides or if there were any islands near by that one might be able to visit because they would not volunteer any information unless you askled. Unfortunately, for my wife and I, there were some front desk staff members that were not aware of such activities and that was the problem we came across. Nonetheless, the hotel itself was fascinating and the room service was very clean and professional, but the beach was horrible and the casino was small and a little out-dated. Although, the night club was nice not many guest attended. However, downtown Ponce and San Juan were interesting historical places to visit. I strongly recommend the rain forest and the trolley rides in the historical place in Ponce and visiting the Monterro Fort in Old San Juan. Overall, My wife and I would consider on going back again with our family if there were some activities within the hotel that would become avialable such as para-sailing, jetskiing, paddle boats, kyaking, banana boat rides, etc. Unfortunately, this hotel didnt have any of these activities or any staff member assigned to direct their guests to any such activities or events that might be of any interest to their guests. So with that said, if you are interested in just relaxing and soaking it all in and doing absolutel nothing, this is the place to go. But, on the otherhand, if you are looking for relaxation and some water activities within the hotel to share and enjoy with your loved one or family members, this is not the place of choice. 
